request.description:
Creates a new user, does the same as the signup (Needs Update)

example of body: 

{
    "email": "testUser@simulados.com",
    "password": "admin",
    "name": "Israel",
    "username": "TestIsrael"
}

return example:

{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Successfully created new user",
    "user": {
        "status": "active",
        "id": 19,
        "email": "testUser@simulados.com",
        "password": "$2a$08$.uKVghF2WeDH6GFNrigBF.VVvP4/LSJni92XZGYNoVFq.bhK0p2Wu",
        "name": "Israel",
        "username": "TestIsrael",
        "updatedAt": "2018-10-27T20:39:08.721Z",
        "createdAt": "2018-10-27T20:39:08.721Z"
    }
}

Delete a user by its id

example of return:

{
    "success": true,
    "message": "User deleted"
}

